and slack off, right?

560
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:11,320
I'm just thirsty.

561
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:13,180
And I want to wet my whistle, okay?

562
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,880
Just let him go.

563
00:35:15,510 --> 00:35:16,920
Every night,

564
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:19,250
he yells about beating Yongchuan Hengjiu.

565
00:35:19,250 --> 00:35:20,540
Who else would be thirsty?

566
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,980
Don't say that, Boss.

567
00:35:22,110 --> 00:35:25,030
If you hadn't forced me to watch the game
in the middle of the night,

568
00:35:25,030 --> 00:35:27,320
I wouldn't have dreamed about Hengjiu.

569
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:29,720
You dreamed about the game?

570
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:30,590
How was it?

571
00:35:31,190 --> 00:35:32,250
Did we win? Tell me.

572
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,920
I didn't dream about the result,

573
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:35,800
but

574
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:38,150
I dreamed of Fang Sulun's big face.

575
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:42,000
Then I was scared awake.

576
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,800
Look at you.

577
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:44,880
Let's go.

578
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,920
To training.

579
00:35:50,550 --> 00:35:52,070
Hurry up.

580
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:53,590
What's the rush?

581
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:56,150
The last one there is a loser.

582
00:35:56,910 --> 00:36:04,880
[Hongjing No. 8 High's Dressing Room]

583
00:36:05,080 --> 00:36:08,370
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

584
00:36:08,190 --> 00:36:09,630
Come on, hurry!

585
00:36:08,370 --> 00:36:11,740
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
versus Yongchuan Hengjiu]

586
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,590
Come on, speed up!

587
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:14,550
Come on, go for it.

588
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:19,280
Qi Liang, mind your arms!

589
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:20,180
Okay, okay.

590
00:36:20,710 --> 00:36:21,710
Come on, go for it.

591
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:22,960
Come on, go for it.

592
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:29,240
What's wrong?

593
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:30,880
Come on.

594
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:31,440
Did you sprain it?

595
00:36:31,440 --> 00:36:32,470
I'm fine.

596
00:36:32,470 --> 00:36:33,550
A little bit.

597
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:35,550
It just hurts a little bit.

598
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:36,360
Endure it.

599
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:37,030
How is it?

600
00:36:39,250 --> 00:36:40,210
A little.

601
00:36:41,810 --> 00:36:42,740
Go back and rest.

602
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:44,610
Ice it for 15 minutes at the hotel.

603
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,890
I'm fine, Coach.

604
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:46,760
I can still train.

605
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:47,670
Go back and rest.

606
00:36:47,670 --> 00:36:49,520
Don't risk a big loss for a small gain.

607
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:50,590
Who shares a room with him?

608
00:36:50,590 --> 00:36:51,200
Me.

609
00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:53,880
Coach, the match is tomorrow.

610
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,610
Because the match is tomorrow,

611
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:57,640
this training isn't important.

612
00:36:57,850 --> 00:36:58,730
Take him back.

613
00:36:58,760 --> 00:36:59,430
Come on.

614
00:37:00,610 --> 00:37:01,510
Let's go, Boss.

615
00:37:03,610 --> 00:37:04,670
Let me do it. Let me.

616
00:37:07,110 --> 00:37:08,960
-Be careful.
-Be careful.

617
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,070
It's fine.

618
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,440
Others continue.

619
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:17,360
How long will this take?

620
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:18,760
Let me carry you, come on.

621
00:37:20,070 --> 00:37:20,880
You carry me?

622
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:22,190
Speed up! Speed up!

623
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:23,920
The match is coming soon.

624
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:26,440
If you get hurt,
I can't afford to compensate you.

625
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:27,400
Be careful!

626
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,530
Don't be like Qin Ao.

627
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:29,910
Chen!

628
00:37:30,080 --> 00:37:31,550
-Come on.
-What's wrong?

629
00:37:31,550 --> 00:37:32,950
Boss sprained his ankle.

630
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:35,060
You should help me
take him back to the hotel.

631
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:36,180
Okay. Let's go.

632
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,800
Are you okay?

633
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:39,920
What could be wrong?

634
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:40,880
Coach just won't let me practice.

635
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:42,420
It's not a big deal today, but

636
00:37:42,420 --> 00:37:44,280
the main thing is the match tomorrow.

637
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,880
You should be more careful.

638
00:37:45,880 --> 00:37:48,030
What could happen to a tough guy like me?

639
00:37:48,030 --> 00:37:49,760
Yeah, but you must be careful.

640
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:51,440
Be careful.

641
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,110
It's fine.

642
00:37:53,110 --> 00:37:54,070
Are you sure
you don't want to go to the hospital

643
00:37:54,070 --> 00:37:55,400
and get some medicine or something?

644
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,550
It's just a minor injury.

645
00:37:56,550 --> 00:37:57,840
It'll heal faster that way.

646
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:58,920
I'm a tough guy.

647
00:37:58,920 --> 00:37:59,920
Stop pretending.

648
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:01,000
Go back and apply ice immediately.

649
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,510
Then I'll get you
some anti-inflammatory medicine.

650
00:38:02,510 --> 00:38:03,920
-Okay.
-It's just that…

651
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:05,320
the match is coming soon.

652
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:07,070
Be a little more careful.

653
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:09,070
Even injured, I can still beat them.

654
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:10,760
Would it kill you not to pretend?

655
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,730
Boss, do you have the room key?

656
00:38:13,070 --> 00:38:14,320
No, I gave it to you.

657
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:17,340
-Look for it.
-I put it right here.

658
00:38:17,510 --> 00:38:18,370
I don't have it.

659
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:23,610
Fang Sulun, what are you doing
in our room?

660
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:25,920
Don't go!

661
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:26,800
-I'll go!
-Catch him!

662
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,030
-Okay, no problem!
-I'll go to the elevator,

663
00:38:28,030 --> 00:38:29,710
-Lu!
-I'll go with you!

664
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,400
Stop right there!

665
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,030
Stop right there!

666
00:38:40,070 --> 00:38:41,200
Stop right there!

667
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,070
Brothers, hurry back.

668
00:38:46,070 --> 00:38:47,870
Our room got broken into. Hurry.

669
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,880
Stop right there!

670
00:38:57,800 --> 00:38:59,600
Where do you think you’re going?

671
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,200
Wait a minute!

672
00:39:06,710 --> 00:39:08,230
You can run, but you can't hide.

673
00:39:08,230 --> 00:39:10,160
Wait for us to catch you at Hengjiu?

674
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,110
Confess, and you'll be treated leniently.

675
00:39:14,110 --> 00:39:15,440
Resist, and you'll be punished severely.

676
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:18,040
Tell the truth,
what were you doing in our room?

677
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:21,510
Why do we need an explanation?

678
00:39:21,510 --> 00:39:22,230
Ms. Lin,

679
00:39:22,230 --> 00:39:23,430
report him directly.

680
00:39:23,510 --> 00:39:25,550
Did Hengjiu send him
to check out our tactics?

681
00:39:25,550 --> 00:39:26,920
Yes, report him directly

682
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:28,550
and disqualify him from the match.

683
00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:29,480
Did he really come

684
00:39:29,480 --> 00:39:30,550
to see our tactics?

685
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:31,710
Are you stupid?

686
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:34,400
They are Yongchuan Hengjiu.

687
00:39:34,630 --> 00:39:36,110
Why would they care about our tactics?

688
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:37,190
Can you hurry

689
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:38,520
and just say something?

690
00:39:38,550 --> 00:39:40,280
If you don't, I'll report you directly.

691
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:41,470
-Don't!
-What are you doing?

692
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:42,030
-What are you doing?
-What are you doing?

693
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:43,150
Let go!

694
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:44,320
-Let them handle it themselves.
-Let go!

695
00:39:44,320 --> 00:39:46,880
Let go!
Stop! What do you want?

696
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:57,550
Lin Lu.

697
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:02,550
Isn't this the ring
you bought for your mom?

698
00:40:03,130 --> 00:40:04,160
Call the police.

699
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:07,110
I-I took the ring.

700
00:40:08,410 --> 00:40:09,740
But this is my own doing.

701
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:12,800
I don't want it to affect my team.

702
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:18,750
This is my mom's ring.

703
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:21,150
Lin Lu bought the ring for his mom.

704
00:40:21,150 --> 00:40:22,800
How did it become your mom's?

705
00:40:25,650 --> 00:40:26,960
This ring

706
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,840
was a birthday present

707
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:31,650
my dad bought my mom when I was 8.

708
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:33,920
Then why was it in the store?

709
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:35,190
Did it fly there?

710
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,930
Because my mom passed away.

711
00:40:44,570 --> 00:40:46,130
What are you talking about?

712
00:40:46,470 --> 00:40:47,590
Make it clear.

713
00:40:52,890 --> 00:40:54,500
Three months after my mom died,

714
00:40:54,500 --> 00:40:55,790
my dad remarried.

715
00:40:56,510 --> 00:40:58,240
The stepmother didn't like me.

716
00:40:58,260 --> 00:40:59,220
She thought

717
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:01,400
I was a third wheel in their marriage.

718
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,190
So my dad

719
00:41:03,190 --> 00:41:05,190
sent me to Hengjiu boarding school.

720
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:07,540
I carried this ring

721
00:41:07,560 --> 00:41:09,120
with me every day.

722
00:41:10,230 --> 00:41:11,800
But when I went to boarding school,
I was afraid of losing it,

723
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:13,800
so I locked it in the cabinet at home.

724
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:16,820
But she must have found it.

725
00:41:17,630 --> 00:41:20,060
She thought it was bad luck
because it was my mom's

726
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:20,940
and sold it.

727
00:41:25,230 --> 00:41:25,840
Later, my dad and I

728
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:27,280
had a fight over it.

729
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:29,510
I pieced together the torn receipt

730
00:41:29,510 --> 00:41:31,710
to find the pre-owned luxury boutique.

731
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,360
But I didn't expect

732
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:34,150
the price...

733
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:36,000
So you got anxious.

734
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:37,320
I've been working to earn money

735
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,880
to buy it back.

736
00:41:38,910 --> 00:41:40,250
But I didn't expect

737
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,970
that you two bought it yesterday.

738
00:41:41,970 --> 00:41:43,970
When I saw you bought it,

739
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:44,920
I don't know what happened to me.

740
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,030
I just went crazy.

741
00:41:46,030 --> 00:41:47,070
I only knew this ring

742
00:41:47,070 --> 00:41:48,590
had to stay with me.

743
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:56,030
But I was desperate.

744
00:41:56,060 --> 00:41:58,000
I was wrong about this.

745
00:41:59,230 --> 00:41:59,900
Lin Lu,

746
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:02,030
I will return the money
for the ring to you.

747
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:03,840
I will give you all my savings.

748
00:42:03,840 --> 00:42:06,100
If it's not enough, I'll write you an IOU.

749
00:42:10,180 --> 00:42:11,220
I'm sorry, Lin Lu.

750
00:42:12,510 --> 00:42:13,230
This is the only thing

751
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:14,920
my mom left me.

752
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,360
I'm sorry.

753
00:42:30,720 --> 00:42:32,520
I can accept any punishment.

754
00:42:33,190 --> 00:42:34,250
I can also drop out.

755
00:42:35,210 --> 00:42:36,960
But I don't want my own business

756
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:38,860
to affect Hengjiu.

757
00:42:45,510 --> 00:42:47,310
Do you have anything else to ask?

758
00:42:51,510 --> 00:42:53,230
You guys decide this matter yourselves.

